title: Encyclopedia of 20th-Century Architecture (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Pdf / English / 1986 / 384 pag / 92.1 MB

The predecessor of this work, the Encyclopaedia of Modern Architecture, was first published in 1963. Now, after an interval of twenty years, a new, expanded and  completely revised version is available.

Originally published in 1964 as Encyclopedia of modern architecture.
Translated and adapted from Knaurs Lexikon der modernen Architektur, edited by [Gerd Hatje and] Wolfgang Pehnt

Completely revised and enlarged ... edition
